{"title":"唱起山歌（外一首）","authors":["华万里"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":10,"day":20}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱起山歌（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华万里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱起山歌，野鹰惊飞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盘旋的时光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在翅上闪烁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光的红栅栏被多次撞碎"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱起山歌，岩壑似梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雄壮的贫困如羽毛凋落"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼眸熠熠闪光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金音符喷出玉米的清香"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱起山歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岁月在农具同时也在乐器"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生生世世的熬炼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从容了我和山村的气魄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱起山歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我像野鹰背负祖辈的回应"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在打谷场的上方放大天空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狂飞狂啸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如注入山民血液的霹雳舞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"归乐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑蹄白蹄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弹响山坡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一群长角的时间冲出黄梅雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岩石咩咩，匆匆应和"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"目的地只要在心上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就会出现在前方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不必再留恋夕阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不必再管教荆棘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泻下一坡黑白的音符"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在天空的脸上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"映一幕乐而知返的归乐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"罕见的芳草地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在自家的栏内"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑蹄白蹄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把纠缠如妖魇的雨韵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弯成角状，轻轻抵磨"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}